url_rewrite.zhimg.com: var m = null; url = url.replace(/\?source=\w+/i,''); if( (m = url.match(/^(https?:\/\/.+\.zhimg\.com\/)(?:\d+\/)?([\w\-]+_)(\w+)(\.(jpg|jpeg|gif|png|bmp|webp))(?:\?.+)?$/i)) ){if(m[3]!='r') {var newUrl = url.replace(url, m[1] + m[2] + 'r' + m[4]); if(call.valid(newUrl)){ url=newUrl;}}}
